name: OIA_Asthma_COPD_Combo_Meds
title: OIA_Asthma_COPD_Combo_Meds
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This value set intends to capture codes for Asthma/COPD combo meds/therapy),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: PHARMACOLOGIC:),(Inclusion Criteria: Contains meds in different strengths, branded, and generic:

SABA/SABA combo
SABA/ICS
LABA/LAMA combo
LABA/ICS
LABA/LAMA/ICSS
MART/MART),(Exclusion Criteria: Single ingredient meds)
